#

Classic Beef Sliders

25 min
$15
250 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

BeefDairy

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

EasyComfort FoodQuick Meal

Description

Juicy beef sliders topped with melted cheese and a tangy sauce, perfect for a quick and satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • ground beef: 1 lb
  • slider buns: 12
  • cheddar cheese: 6 slices
  • pickles: 1/2 cup
  • ketchup: 1/4 cup
  • mustard: 2 tbsp
  • onion: 1, minced
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
